'''Woodweal''' is a monster-only spell which heals <code>34 + 1d(3 * [[HD]])</code> HP to the caster.<ref>{{source ref|0.30.0|mon-cast.cc|5741}}</ref> It can only be used if a [[tree]] is adjacent to the caster.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.27]], Woodweal would destroy a tree on use.
*This spell was added in [[0.26]].

